  m_text: 'CONGRATULATIONS! You found the watch..



    The city never changed.


    Your
    perception did.


    By slowing down and reconnecting with the present moment,

    you
    inverted the cycle of anxiety.


    The watch symbolizes the time you reclaimed
    from anxiety.


    Thank you for playing! :)'
